data.description: PRICE REDUCED $40,000 FOR A RAPID SALE!  Fall Season in the beautiful mountains of Rim country takes the everyday stress away, with Wildlife wandering by this home, providing daily entertainment.  Spacious screened front porch is perfect for spending the days enjoying the peaceful forest that surrounds you. Well cared for home for many years. Single level main living area, Renovated walk-out basement adds another bath, with storage under stairs & gas stove for the cool months. NEW entry steps & back exit deck. Shed wired for electric +window A/C (perfect for a gym, workshop or hobby room). Two RV pads, Over-sized garage with workbench. Lots of room for recreational vehicle parking, plus tons of storage.
